metadata.name: Generational Wealth
metadata.description:
Inspired by Matt Furie & the launch of Pepecoin. 

This artwork is a beautiful and mesmerizing mixed media creation that combines the soft strokes of oil pastels with the rough textures of paper & collage techniques.

The colours used are predominantly pastel shades, creating a dreamlike/nostalgic atmosphere that evokes a sense of calm and contemplation.

The meme can't be stopped!

We only know green.
